tourBios.curYrHigh: Joined PGA TOUR Latinoamérica after claiming runner-up honors at the Argentina Q-School in January.
tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Claimed low amateur honors with a T16 finish at the Personal Classic on his first career start on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica. Had entered the event via the Monday Qualifier.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Played college golf at Wichitta State University (2011-15)... Named 2014 Missouri Valley Conference (MVC) Golfer of the Year, Three-time All-Conference in 2012, 2013 and 2014... 2012 MVC Freshman of the Year... Placed second at the 2010 Doral Publix Junior Classic... Won the French Junior Championship in 2006.
tourBios.personal: His favorite professional team is Paris Saint-Germain FC... Would like to trade places for a day with Arnold Palmer... Personal motto is "Get it done, no excuses."... Instagram name is @louiscohenboyer
tourBios.exmtStatus: Exempt - Finished 2-11 at 2016 Q-School (exempt to midseason reshuffle)
